evarūpo manoviññeyyo dhammo na sevitabbo … 
evarūpo manoviññeyyo dhammo sevitabbo. 
‘Manoviññeyyaṁ dhammampāhaṁ, sāriputta, duvidhena vadāmi—
sevitabbampi, asevitabbampī’ti—
